OL,4,Cassault in Jersey
OL,6,F's Royal Court has convicted a man for
OL,7,Ftwo counts of rape and two counts of
OL,8,Fcommon assault.
OL,10,FDavid Nigel Pearce was found guilty
OL,11,Fafter a "detailed investigation" and a
OL,12,F10-day trail.
OL,14,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,15,FConstable Verity Thomas, praised the
OL,16,Fvictim for having the bravery to speak
OL,17,Fup. She said "It is down to her
OL,18,Fcourage that he has been convicted
OL,19,Ftoday (1 March 2024).
